              <div class="per">Local SEO · $167/mo bundle</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it delivers</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Weekly GBP posts, photos, and review reply suggestions</li>
                <li>Weekly rank, calls, and direction-request reporting</li>
                <li>Bundle adds blog SEO + social automation at $167/mo</li>
                <li>One invoice, no multi-tool sprawl</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
