            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Single-location operators who want GBP managed alongside content SEO.</div>
            <a href="/checkout/" class="tool-cta-btn">Start at $49/mo →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">02</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Merchynt (Paige)</div>
