              <div class="price">$89<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Per location</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it delivers</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>AI agent that posts, replies, and optimizes weekly</li>
                <li>Suggests services, products, and Q&amp;A updates</li>
